project_descr: Women in selected areas exercise their electoral rights and participate in voting  and are empowered to run as candidates during local elections

outputs.output_descr: The project aims at increasing women’s participation, including from minorities and youth groups, at elections, both as candidates and peaceful voters, in priority geographic areas under currently ongoing PRF projects.
